title: Jug, 1986-61-182, ca. 1800–10
provenance: Delomosne and Son, Ltd;, London; 1966 Phelps Warren, NY
description: Oval straight-sided body with extended pouring and in-turned top lip; wide loop handle notched; sides cut with 2 encircled stars either side of handle, around the front wit a band of diamonds. flutes above; heavy' glass clear.
